	  Clean up some includes, and packing options.

	* app/BladeMap.cpp, app/BladeMap.h, app/ClientConnection.h,
	  app/IsoMap.cpp, app/IsoMap.h, app/NewServerWindow.h, app/Texture.h,
	  app/Tile.h, app/TileMap.h, app/debug.h app/Vector3D.h:
	  Remove obsolete files from the build.

	* app/GL.h: Switch to using visual/GL.h from apogee.

