	  NewLayerWindow to use the Gtk Dialog base class.

	* app/Server.cpp, app/WorldEntity.cpp, app/WorldEntity.h:
	  Switch to using World Entity factory code from apogee.

	* app/ServerEntities.cpp, app/ServerEntities.h: Switch import
	  and export dialogs to using Dialog base class. Modify world
	  render interface to match the interface used in apogee. Adapt
	  for new apogee entity classes.

	* app/Terrain.cpp, app/Terrain.h:
	  Add new constructor to handle the case if terrain is managed by
	  the entity renderer rather than this layer.

	* app/Terrain.cpp: Remove use of obsolete extensions.

	* app/equator_plugin.cpp: Load config for apogee code.

