	* app/ServerEntities.h, app/ServerEntities.cpp: Add windows for
	  import and export options.

	* app/ViewWindow.h: Remove unnecessary debugging output.

2002-05-02  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/InheritanceWindow.h, app/LayerWindow.h, app/NewLayerWindow.h,
	  app/NewServerWindow.h, app/Palette.h, app/ServerWindow.h,
	  app/ViewWindow.h: Added handler for attempt to close window,
	  so windows which are permanent are just hidden, and view windows
	  cannot be closed.

	* app/ServerEntities.cpp, app/ServerEntities.h: Added beginnings
	  of code for handling importing and exporting of atlas files
	  full of entities.

2002-04-30  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/ServerEntities.cpp: Made selection verification in the
	  case of multiple selected entities behave more sanely.

2002-04-30  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/ServerEntities.cpp, app/ServerEntities.h: Implemented
	  rubberband selection of server entities, and highlighting
	  multiple selected entities.

2002-04-29  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/BladeMap.h, app/EntityLayer.h, app/GlView.cpp,
	  app/HeightManager.h, app/Holo.h, app/IsoMap.h,
	  app/Layer.h, app/Model.cpp, app/Model.h, app/types.h:
	  Added general purpose alignment mechanism, so the
	  selection can be aligned with things like grids, or
	  heightfields.

	* app/ServerEntities.cpp, app/ServerEntities.h: Implemented aligning
	  with heighfield for selected entity.

2002-04-26  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/BladeMap.cpp, app/IsoMap.cpp: Modify coal calls to use new
	  lower case method names.

	* app/GlView.cpp: Disable accumulation buffer animation hack
	  until an alternative can be found that performs better.

2002-04-25  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/BladeMap.cpp, app/BladeMap.h, app/IsoMap.cpp, app/IsoMap.h:
	  Catch up with coals modified API, in Coal namespace.

