	* app/BladeMap.cpp, app/BladeMap.h: Re-wrote blade renderer to use
	  new coal API.

	* app/IsoMap.cpp, app/IsoMap.h: Re-wrote iso processing code to
	  use new coal API.

2002-04-24  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/GlView.cpp, app/Server.h: Removed obsolete code which
	  still relied on old Eris types.

	* app/IsoMap.cpp, app/HeightManager.cpp, app/GlView.cpp:
	  gcc 3 fixes.

2002-04-22  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/Server.cpp: Fix for new Eris polling interface.

2002-04-12  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/GlView.cpp, app/GlView.h, app/Model.cpp, app/Model.h,
	  app/ViewWindow.cpp, app/ViewWindow.h:
	  Move cursor position into model, so there it is no longer one
	  cursor per view. Implement necessary signals etc. Add z coord
	  indicator to cursor.

	* app/HeightMap.h, app/HeightMap.cpp, app/HeightManager.cpp:
	  Implement libpng based heightmap loader, implement loading
	  of heightmap sections based on cursor position, and tidy
	  up boundary conditions.

2002-04-10  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/ServerEntities.cpp: Ensure bbox is only drawn if the entity
	  has one.

	* app/Server.h: Use new Eris Log.h for log definitions.

	* app/Server.cpp: Use Eris::Logged to get log messages.

2002-04-03  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/Texture.h, app/Texture.cpp: Give tiles a name, add support for
	  rendering them on a heightmap, and outlining them.

	* app/ServerEntities.h, app/Model.h, app/Model.cpp, app/Layer.h,
	  app/IsoMap.h, app/Holo.h, app/EntityLayer.h, app/BladeMap.h:
	  Add new export method to layer interface.

	* app/NewLayerWindow.cpp, app/Model.h, app/Model.cpp,
	  HeightData.cpp, HeightData.h, HeightMap.cpp, HeightMap.h,
	  app/HeightManager.cpp, app/HeightManager.h:
	  Add heightdata class which is bound to a model, and stores
	  height data associated with that model. Add new heightmanager
	  layer, which is used to manipulate the height data attached to
	  the model.

	* app/MainWindow.cpp, app/LayerWindow.cpp: Include pixmaps at compile
	  time instead of loading them at runtime.

	* app/IsoMap.h, app/IsoMap.cpp, app/TileMap.h, app/TileMap.cpp,
	  app/types.h: Switch to storing tiles in
	  a TileMap class for efficiency, and add support for selecting
	  tiles, and displaying them highlighted using marching ants.
	  Add header file for some typedefs used in this code, for
	  reuse elsewhere.

	* app/Holo.cpp: Tweak background grid so it switches to lower
	  density if zoomed out too far.

	* app/GlView.h: Add accessors so an idea of the view size can be
	  obtained when rendering.

	* app/GlView.cpp: Set up GL context to have an accumulation buffer,
	  and use it to store rendered scene, so that animated effects
	  like marching ants can be done without having to re-render the
	  whole scene every frame. Use accumulation buffer for updating
	  cursor effects like drag selection. Add new tool submenus for
	  adding extra tools.

	* configure.in: Fix building as a standalone app, if gimp is not
	  available.

2002-03-14  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/BladeMap.h, app/GlView.cpp, app/GlView.h, app/Holo.h,
	  app/IsoMap.h, app/Layer.h:
	  Added animate method to all layers. Call it regularly to
	  animate the view, and provide a cycling value between 0
	  and 1 to control cycling animations. Use the accumulation
	  buffer to store rendered frame once complete, and then overlay
	  animations onto stored frame to avoid having to re-render
	  when animating.

	* app/ServerEntities.h, app/ServerEntities.cpp: Use animation
	  mechanism to animate marching ants on selected entities.

2002-03-13  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/ServerEntities.h, app/ServerEntities.cpp, app/GlView.h,
	  app/GlView.cpp: Highlight selection using an as yet unanimated
	  marching ants style outline.

2002-03-04  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/ServerEntities.h, app/ServerEntities.cpp: Added hook
	  so that screen is refreshed everytime something is updated or
	  moved.

	* app/ServerEntities.h, app/ServerEntities.cpp, app/Server.h,
	  app/Server.cpp, app/Layer.h, app/IsoMap.h, app/Holo.h,
	  app/GlView.cpp, app/EntityLayer.h, app/BladeMap.h:
	  Migrate to new wfmath based Eris API, and use wfmath types
	  internally.

