2001-12-19  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/Model.h, app/Model.cpp: Class that stores the world model,
	  extracted from GlView class so that model and view are separate,
	  allowing multiple views of a single model.

	* app/ViewWindow.h, app/ViewWindow.cpp, app/NewLayerWindow.h,
	  app/NewLayerWindow.cpp, app/MainWindow.h, app/MainWindow.cpp,
	  app/LayerWindow.h, app/LayerWindow.cpp, app/Layer.h,
