	  Cleaned up window layout.

	* app/equator_plugin.cpp: Added elaoration so it is clear that gimp
	  plugin error is not a problem.

2001-12-18  Al Riddoch  <alriddoch@zepler.org>

	* app/AtlasMapWidget.cpp, app/BladeMap.cpp, app/GlView.cpp,
	  app/IsoMap.cpp, app/LayerWindow.cpp, app/MainWindow.cpp,
